# orgs/ is fully ignored (line 15) — the public install repo ships ZERO real org
# data. Operators create their own org during onboarding. The prior carve-outs
# that re-included orgs/<org>/docs/durable/**, knowledge.md, and research-artifacts/
# leaked AscendOps-internal confidential data (vendor PII, EIN, durable specs) into
# this PUBLIC repo; removed 2026-06-02 (install fast-follow). If shipped reference
# doctrine is wanted later, add a sanitized orgs/example/ — never a real org.

